name: The Hierophant
description:
The Hierophant has the uncanny ability to sniff out those who have the spark of magic within them and has psionic powers that allow her to (among other things) communicate with some of the less human denizens of the colony. She also is the self-crowned ruler of a small crew of Witchez, a coven of teen girls with latent magic ability that seeks to eventually usurp the Queen. 

Created as part of the Vessels GEN-0 art/fiction competition by the creator of Witchez.xyz
